title: Mytheon
notes: Game starts up in borderless-fullscreen. Sound works. Menus work. However it cannot connect to the main server, sits on waiting for characters indefinitely.

Game installs and loads to main menu without issue.  However, the game is unable to retrieve the player's characters: the game stalls at "retrieving characters."  Choosing to quit the retrieval generates the message "server unavailable."  The game also crashes when quitting to desktop.
